==Introduction==
The '''URL Type''' represents a URL path (hyperlink).

The Wiki Automation Tool supports editing, viewing and searching on the URL properties.


==Definition==

The URL Property extends a common definition of the [[Help:Property|Property Definition]] with the following elements:

<pre>
<property ... size={SIZE}>
</property>
</pre>

{| class="helptable"
|-
! {SIZE}
| A length of the input field. Default value: 80.
|}


==Semantic database==
The URL Property is implemented as a [[Special:Types/URL]] MediaWiki datatype.


==Example==
<pre>
<property name="Link" type="URL" label="Link" attribute="link">
  <description>A Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) to identify a name or a web resource.</description>
  <instruction/>
</property>
</pre>


==User Interface==
* '''View Page'''
The property displays a value as a hyperlink.

* '''Edit Page'''
The property provides one line text input field.
A length of the field is controlled by the 'size' attribute.

* '''Search Page'''
The property allows user to a choose search operator from the following options: ''Starts with, Contains, Equals, Ends with, Has any value''
and allows user to enter a desired url path in one line text input field.
